#include <cstdio>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;

int main () {

	int t;
	scanf ("%d",&t);

	int x1,y1,x2,y2;
	int a1,b1,a2,b2;
	while (t--) {

		scanf ("%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d",&x1,&y1,&x2,&y2,&a1,&b1,&a2,&b2);

		int X1 = max(x1,a1);
		int Y1 = max(y1,b1);
		int X2 = min(x2,a2);
		int Y2 = min(y2,b2);
	
		if (X1 < X2 && Y1 < Y2) printf("%d %d %d %d\n",X1,Y1,X2,Y2);
		else printf("No Overlap\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
